		<td><b>Really Noob question</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I understand that you code a game in assembler, but how do you get from that to the .Rom file that you can play on an emulator?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
